<item>
            <title>[LU-1678] Panic when a file created with O_LOV_DELAY_CREAT is opened by fid</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1678</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;create a file without a lov (O_LOV_DELAY_CREATE)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;open it through .lustre/fid/...... path&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Attached is a sanity.sh patch which introduces a new test to reproduce the bug&lt;br/&gt;
I will create a gerrit with the reproducer&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="15326">LU-1678</key>
            <summary>Panic when a file created with O_LOV_DELAY_CREAT is opened by fid</summary>
